definitions.definition: An inner city area of Glasgow , Glasgow council area, Scotland , south of the Clyde ( OS grid ref NS5664 ) .
A city in the Hunter Region of New South Wales , Australia , west of Newcastle .
A local government area in New South Wales , Australia , which includes the actual city; in full, the City of Cessnock .
